== 國際組織 ==
=== 世界衛生組織 ===
[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]的緊急委員會在[[日內瓦|日內瓦]]召開會議，鑒於墨西哥疫情向全球發出全球緊急狀態<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/trad/hi/newsid_8010000/newsid_8017900/8017907.stm|title="豬流感" 世衛宣布全球緊急狀態|publisher=BBC新聞|date=2009-04-25|accessdate=2009-04-26|archive-date=2009-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090428112631/http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/trad/hi/newsid_8010000/newsid_8017900/8017907.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月27日，世衛再召開會議，把警戒級別從第三級提升至第四級，即病毒可以在人與人之間傳播<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/simp/hi/newsid_8020000/newsid_8021800/8021815.stm|title=世卫组织提高甲型流感(H1N1)警戒级别|publisher=BBC新聞|date=2009-04-27|accessdate=2009-04-28|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927103256/http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/simp/hi/newsid_8020000/newsid_8021800/8021815.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="who_statement_20090427">{{cite news|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/news/statements/2009/h1n1_20090427/zh/index.html|title=豬流感|publisher=世界衛生組織|author=陳馮富珍|date=2009-04-27|accessdate=2009-04-28|archive-date=2014-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140204040956/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/news/statements/2009/h1n1_20090427/zh/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月29日，更把警戒级别提升至第五級，即强烈地显示即将发生流感大流行<ref name="cnn_who_raises_20090429">{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2009/HEALTH/04/29/swine.flu/index.html|title=WHO raises pandemic alert to second-highest level|publisher=CNN.com|date=2009-04-29|accessdate=2009-04-29|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126050546/http://www.cnn.com/2009/HEALTH/04/29/swine.flu/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

6月11日，正式將警戒級別提升至最高的第六級<ref>{{cite news|url=http://app2.rthk.org.hk/pda/news/content.php?id=588469|title="世衞將全球流感大流行警戒級別升至6級。|publisher=世衞將全球流感大流行警戒級別升至6級date=2009-06-10|accessdate=2009-06-10}}{{dead link|date=十一月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>。

