4月26日，加拿大東岸[[新斯科舍省|新斯科舍省]]的{{tsl|en|King's-Edgehill School|國王中學艾吉爾分校}}有四名學生被發現感染到H1N1甲型流感病毒。他們年齡界于12到18歲之间，病情溫和。其中一位學生曾參加[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]東南部的[[尤卡坦半島|尤卡坦半島]]的遊學團<ref name="g_ap_0426">{{cite news|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5g-G1kSAM9yaH00eBrXD2S5s-3ZhgD97Q9LPG0|title=Canada confirms 4 swine flu cases among students|publisher=Google/AP|date=2009-04-26|accessdate=2009-04-27|archive-date=2009-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090503031625/http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5g-G1kSAM9yaH00eBrXD2S5s-3ZhgD97Q9LPG0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同時，[[英屬哥倫比亞省|英屬哥倫比亞省]]的[[低陸平原|低陸平原]]地區亦有兩名年齡界乎25到35歲的男子被發現感染到此病毒。他們最近由墨西哥返回加國，並且已經完全康復
<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/story/RTGAM.20090426.wswineflucanada0426/BNStory/National/home|publisher=The Globe and Mail|title=Swine flu confirmed in Canada|date=2009-04-26|accessdate=2009-04-27|archive-date=2009-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090501082403/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/story/RTGAM.20090426.wswineflucanada0426/BNStory/National/home/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

4月28日，[[艾伯塔|艾伯塔]]省政府在[[埃德蒙顿|埃德蒙顿]]宣布在艾伯塔省确证2例甲型流感H1N1病毒。

[[加拿大|加拿大]][[安大略|安大略]]省公共衛生局傳染性疾病預防與控制主任[[麥可·賈當|賈當]]博士（Dr Michael Gardam）在[[加拿大廣播公司|加拿大廣播公司]]的訪問中表示，縱使豬流感疫情在安大略省爆發也不會像2003年的[[SARS|SARS]]那樣嚴重<ref name = "r_canada">{{cite news | title = Swine flu not as serious as SARS: Canada's Ontario | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/newsOne/idUSTRE53N4PB20090424 | accessdate = 2009-07-11 | archive-date = 2009-04-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090427110026/http://www.reuters.com/article/newsOne/idUSTRE53N4PB20090424 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。為了預防病毒演變成全國流行，加拿大公共衛生局跟從世界衛生組織來評定警戒級別<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.phac-aspc.gc.ca/cpip-pclcpi/index-eng.php |title=Public Health Agency of Canada: The Canadian Pandemic Influenza Plan for the Health Sector |accessdate=2009-07-11 |archive-date=2009-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090521172412/http://www.phac-aspc.gc.ca/cpip-pclcpi/index-eng.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。除了蒙特利爾醫院報告有兩個懷疑感染豬流感的人士，正在接受隔離觀察，他們都是從墨西哥返回加拿大後感到不適。其後，全部測試結果呈現陰性反應<ref name="gazette">{{cite web |url=http://www.montrealgazette.com/Health/Swine+fears+Lakeshore+General+unfounded/1534676/story.html |title=Swine-flu fears at Lakeshore General unfounded |publisher=[[The_Gazette_(Montreal)|The Gazette]] (Montreal) |date=2009-04-25 |accessdate=2009-04-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090427135648/http://www.montrealgazette.com/Health/Swine+fears+Lakeshore+General+unfounded/1534676/story.html |archivedate=2009-04-27 }}</ref>。而加拿大東岸[[新斯科舍省|新斯科舍省]]的一批學生則正在測試是否染有豬流感<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/world/story/2009/04/25/flu-mexico-090425.html|title=Swine flu outbreak international 'public health emergency': WHO|publisher=[[CBC_News|CBC News]]|date=2009-04-25|5=|accessdate=2009-04-25|archive-date=2010-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100909161713/http://www.cbc.ca/world/story/2009/04/25/flu-mexico-090425.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

加拿大的實驗室協助墨西哥政府確診其中18個個案<ref name="who2009-04-24">{{cite web|url=http://www.who.int/csr/don/2009_04_24/en/index.html|title=Influenza-Like Illness in the United States and Mexico|publisher=[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]|date=2009-04-24|accessdate=2009-04-25|archive-date=2009-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090427070549/http://www.who.int/csr/don/2009_04_24/en/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

